Notes: SP opened up 10-2 lead on eight points by Nechuta and never trailed...LC cut
lead to 45-40 with 16:31 left before a 15-0 SP run as LC missed ten straight
shots...SP's Scott scored six straight points for 71-49 lead with 6:21 left.
